
INSTALL

  To install:
  $ make
  $ sudo make install

  By default it will be under /usr/local.
  To change this behaviour specify the installation directory:
  $ sudo make install DESTDIR=/opt


SUDOERS

  Add a line with your user or group in sudoers(8):
  <user_or_group>  ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: /usr/local/share/safe-crux/scx


PACKAGES

  To create a CRUX package and install them just run:
  $ pkgmk
  $ sudo pkgadd safe-crux#VERSION-RELEASE.pkg.tar.xz
